Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是近江神宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参拜的礼节是鞠躬两次 拍手两次 再鞠躬一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可能会觉得这些规矩形式什么的很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但神明的心胸不一定是宽广的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨守礼仪 许下你们的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不奢望奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保佑大家不要发生意外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保佑大家发挥出练习时的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.03,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}比赛场地是在其他地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:55.82,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是的 在旁边那座叫「劝学馆」的楼里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走啦 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:01:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿好像有个全部参赛者集合起来参拜的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 所有人又要一起来这儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于来到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江神宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然一如往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绫濑同学就是女王了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:53.11,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(864,811)\pos(490,301)}初春入田野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好热啊 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要穿袴了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的全国大会 就让我们正装上阵吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会场里好像是有空调的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛的衣服交给妈妈我来帮他穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那千早的衣服呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是已经穿好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她不动也不说话 所以看起来还像是个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在E组啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 里边没有超强的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据瘦子的资料所言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意的是静冈的富士崎高中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.16,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是哪个? 是哪些人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地的善德寺高中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.75,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我看看我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表福井的国弥高中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年在预赛赢了北央
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷新…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有报名参加明天的个人赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的就是东京代表队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 据说他们赢了北央学园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击败北央的须藤的人是哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 须藤输了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们社团真的才组建了3个月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多强啊
Comment: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{画面注}佐贺县代表 武知高校 特点: 歌留多部建立8年,去年打入全国赛,也进入淘汰赛,在第一轮被淘汰.其他时候没有过更好的成绩.需要注意的是B级的井上龙平和田中彩子二人.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们首战的对手 是佐贺的武知高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很强吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很强吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有两人是B级 其他人没有段位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的顺序怎么排?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照对阵北央时一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理 那是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我当弃子就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和最强的家伙对战!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 那怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我输了 剩下四人赢了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能提高获胜概率的话 我什么都肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要晋级!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是东京代表啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书桌小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得分能手大多会排在两端和正中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.57,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.87,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那驹野在最前 接着是大江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:10.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有大家在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要晋级!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家齐心协力!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请大家摆好牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:03.42,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}なにわずに　さくやこのはな　ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:03.42,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「花映难波津 隆冬且暂隐」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:12.01,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:12.01,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多帅气的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录记录
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子实力有多强呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:24.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:24.15,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 连我都紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.32,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あけぬれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「冬晓催人散…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.41,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}たきのおとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.41,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「飞练余枯影…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点放松下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张一张地抢到手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袴好热啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明啊 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是向您祈求过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过「请保佑大家不要发生意外」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我并不奢求奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走错路了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明来过几次了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为每次都是坐车来的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘫痪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是身体右边部分变得比较难以活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 你可能会被吓到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么? 爷爷就是爷爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爷爷 新来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是爷爷啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 我给你做了全新的摆法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿纸记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牌都要乱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷不会认输的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正努力只用左手也能抢牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滋贺县的近江神宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我们也送上现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:49.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}挑战三连霸的名人三木先生的 是周防久志选手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷啊 名人战是什么样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}周防选手是在校的大学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷也会紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过会在比赛前让我摆好造型拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点成了明星的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 去想象一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象自己正身处那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯光很亮很热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许许多多人看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前是最强的名人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能听见拍打榻榻米的声音的近江劝学馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想象一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会获胜的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是轻微的发作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爷爷的心脏比较弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说观察一下 明天就可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 吓我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还坐上了救护车…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑部发现萎缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是早期的痴呆症状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新! 新!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说翔二在昨天的大会拿了冠军 升到A级了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为最先拿到的绝对应该是你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过你比赛和练习都没有参加…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是没办法的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}翔二 我说你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然以前你的名人爷爷让你很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在可是反过来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该觉得要是没有他 就有时间练习了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老师!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:29.83,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}上啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「升上C级了」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也在好好努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然信里说自己加入了田径部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.47,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz17.921\a5\move(408,384,408,454)}新也一定在努力吧 \N我们有机会再比试吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周星期天中午 我有个同学聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你照顾爷爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽早回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈头发白了不少啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的 会洒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把袴拿出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得去福井大会!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 今年你不用去参加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不去?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 恢复以前的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么「但是」!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能把大会丢在一边 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爷爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 爸爸中午过后就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想落在大家后面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点升上A级!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想象一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳鸣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻…要进攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样结束!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑弃权
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 借过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 千早怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有四个人 我们也会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是绫濑同学的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她去等候室 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能输…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样结束的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你得躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛已经弃权了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弃权…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 都说不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老实呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了也没用 你已经不能重回比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干 我不干!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明努力过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家约好了…要赢下来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跟以前一样的直率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在思考着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于歌留多和…爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去市民医院的急诊室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉真岛同学他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩在比赛中好像就一直身体不适
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望没什么大碍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不是绵谷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是联盟的…吉冈老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从去年开始你就没有参加过任何大会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个大会你参加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.47,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能再见到绵谷老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的歌留多 和绵谷老师一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 比赛也差不多要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢…歌留多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太离谱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太离谱了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 为什么北央的人会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我报名参加了明天的个人战啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 因身体不适而弃权算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是以东京代表的身份出赛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 你以为哭就能得到原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人以为东京的实力很弱的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 不用躺着休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这是做什么呢 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好道歉的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑 我今天第一次获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 而且还是二连胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和对方都还剩七张的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜中了 抢到了「秋色」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.87,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(785,658)}しら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那一张决定了胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在复赛的淘汰赛中输给了富士崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好想再赛几场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体状态不能马上恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭明早第一班新干线回去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到现在还按捺不住兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以完美的身体状态迎战明天的个人赛!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天能出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…今天我真的是很没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是…让新失望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想让他看看我出色的表现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你好重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 不会吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为会很轻 结果重得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新拜托负责管理的吉冈老师转交给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是福井的特产
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:03.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\fn楷体\shad0\bord0\c&H65757D&}下次在比赛中见 新
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达给新了
